==Northern Kurdish==
===Etymology===
From {{inh|kmr|ira-pro|*kanati}}, from {{inh|kmr|iir-pro|*karnati}}, from {{der|kmr|ine-pro|*keh₂n-}}. Compare {{cog|fa|خواندن|tr=xândan}}, {{cog|la|canō}}, {{m|la|cantō}}, {{cog|cy|canu}}.
